section_title: Purpose of the Test Case Document
text: [Provide the purpose of the Test Case Document. This document should be tailored to fit a particular projectâ€™s needs.]The Test Case document documents the functional requirements of the <test case title> test case. The intended audience is the project manager, project team, and testing team. Some portions of this document may on occasion be shared with the client/user and other stakeholder whose input/approval into the testing process is needed.
